member.remarks:
Sample request:

    GET /getallsites

Sample response:

    {
        "respcode": 1200,
        "description": "Successful",
        "sites": [
            {
                "siteId": 1,
                "siteName": "Novade Office",
                "siteDescription": "Novade Pte. Ltd. main office"
            },
            {
                ...
            }
            ...
        ]
    }

Response codes:
    1200 = "Successful"
    1201 = "Error"
